title: Apple M1 series vs Intel Core i9-12900HK: Which laptop CPU is better?
content:
Intel’s new Alder Lake processors have created a huge wave in the industry with some impressive performance numbers on the board. As we mentioned in our review of the Core i9-12900HK, it’s one of the most powerful chips out there right now. In fact, even other processors in Alder Lake H-series are looking very promising.

The post Apple M1 series vs Intel Core i9-12900HK: Which laptop CPU is better? appeared first on xda-developers.
description: In this article, we're going to take a look at the Apple M1 vs Intel Core i9-12900HK comparison to find out which laptop CPU is better.
